import product_logo from '../assets/images/coffee_bag.png'

export const products = [
    {id: 0, name:'Borbón Rosado', weight: '250 gr', image: product_logo}, 
    {id: 1, name: 'Queen Geisha', weight: '500 gr', image: product_logo},
    {id: 2, name: 'Caturra', weight: '250 gr', image: product_logo},
    {id: 3, name: 'Pacamara', weight: '500 gr', image: product_logo},
    {id: 4, name: 'Jember', weight: '500 gr', image: product_logo},
